came to the Suhan meridians.



The broken dragon vein, Su Han never thought to repair.



What does the repair do? It will only hinder Su Han's cultivation.



This so-called 'dragon vein', is just what these stupid people in the mainland of Longwu think, the Su Han of the last life, training is not this bullshit dragon vein, but meridians!
